<br>
Otherwise, I'm really happy with the ruleset.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=castinareleas>CastinarEleas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/18/01 12:13:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=921.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Change?</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> 2. Languages -- Thieves' Cant should be strictly rogue only *agreed* (As to the rest.. I thought it WAS group only to learn, dont' think /say works.)<br>
