<br>
I agree with your idea of the grouping as well --- it opens some RP possibilities that will completely be restricted otherwise.  <br>
<br>
For myself, I'm content working around the buff/heal problems (make the grouping a bit more difficult, but more worthwhile when it is successful, IMO <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
